query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `documentEntities` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `documentId` int NOT NULL,
  `entityType` varchar(64) NOT NULL,
  `entityValue` varchar(512) NOT NULL,
  `normalizedValue` varchar(512),
  `occurrenceCount` int DEFAULT 1,
  `firstOccurrence` int,
  `confidence` int,
  `extractorModel` varchar(128),
  `metadata` text,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `documentEntities_documentId_idx` (`documentId`),
  KEY `documentEntities_entityType_idx` (`entityType`),
  KEY `documentEntities_entityValue_idx` (`entityValue`),
  CONSTRAINT `documentEntities_documentId_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`documentId`) REFERENCES `documents` (`id`) ON DELETE CASCADE
);
